{"title":"Hello World","date":"2020-01-21T02:11:20.124Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 21, 2020","L":"01/21/2020","MM-DD":"01-21"},"link":"2020/01/21/hello-world","updated":"2020-02-03T06:57:46.676Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/21/hello-world#Quick-Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2>\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/21/hello-world#Create-a-new-post\"></a>Create a new post</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/21/hello-world#Run-server\"></a>Run server</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/21/hello-world#Generate-static-files\"></a>Generate static files</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/21/hello-world#Deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"function-point","link":"2020/01/22/postName"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/01/21/hello-world/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"Quick-Start","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"Create-a-new-post","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"Run-server","index":"1.2"},{"title":"","id":"Generate-static-files","index":"1.3"},{"title":"","id":"Deploy-to-remote-sites","index":"1.4"}]}]}